    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Omega Crafter》是一款开放世界生存制造游戏，游戏世界的开发因为一个神秘程序的干预而陷入困境。玩家可以携手可编程伙伴Grammi，与其他玩家共同探险，建造城市，挑战强大的敌人，体验属于每个人独一无二的乐趣！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >来吧，击败那些怪物和头目吧！ </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >似乎是有不少怪物和Boss在给游戏开发制造混乱哦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grammi会帮助我们一起收集材料打造超强武器，让我们共同努力打败那些强大的头目吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262080/extras/57370596c6d155336daf6d94b9559102.poster.avif?t=1747276827\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262080/extras/57370596c6d155336daf6d94b9559102.webm?t=1747276827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262080/extras/57370596c6d155336daf6d94b9559102.mp4?t=1747276827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >用编程来指导Grammi吧！ </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grammi的各种动作，从采矿，伐木，搬运到制作，乃至舞蹈，都能以编程的方式轻松实现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有什么想让Grammi帮忙的事情吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262080/extras/019703f5f273a8ab8f6830b4d6b0cf66.poster.avif?t=1747276827\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262080/extras/019703f5f273a8ab8f6830b4d6b0cf66.webm?t=1747276827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262080/extras/019703f5f273a8ab8f6830b4d6b0cf66.mp4?t=1747276827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一同打造属于我们城市吧！ </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个世界中，存在各式各样的资源，从常见的石头，木材到未曾见过的奇特物质。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与Grammi一起，让我们利用自动化的操作建设出理想的城市！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262080/extras/b66887940cf47f662b78b22124cc49e8.poster.avif?t=1747276827\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262080/extras/b66887940cf47f662b78b22124cc49e8.webm?t=1747276827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262080/extras/b66887940cf47f662b78b22124cc49e8.mp4?t=1747276827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一起探索这个未知的世界吧！ </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Omega Crafter》中有多种多样的生物群系，玩家将会见到不同的风景，怪物，资源，甚至是那些被隐藏的秘密。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与Grammi和朋友们一同踏上这趟冒险的旅程吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262080/extras/f6ec6e9245f8b074c3518ba4bbe8fcc1.poster.avif?t=1747276827\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262080/extras/f6ec6e9245f8b074c3518ba4bbe8fcc1.webm?t=1747276827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262080/extras/f6ec6e9245f8b074c3518ba4bbe8fcc1.mp4?t=1747276827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >和朋友们一起体验这款游戏吧！ </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >既可以一人探索，也可以叫上朋友们一起挑战强大的头目。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个由代码生成的辽阔世界里，随心所欲地畅游吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262080/extras/48a47e18aa88395ff399fc0733b3d57d.poster.avif?t=1747276827\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262080/extras/48a47e18aa88395ff399fc0733b3d57d.webm?t=1747276827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262080/extras/48a47e18aa88395ff399fc0733b3d57d.mp4?t=1747276827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
